@startuml
title Telecom DID / VC / VP — Cryptographic Summary

skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor #f9f9f9
  BorderColor #555555
  FontSize 12
}

actor "Subscriber (Holder)\n did:telco:harishm" as H
participant "Telco Operator (Issuer)\n did:telco:airtel" as I
participant "Service Verifier (Verifier)\n did:telco:verifier" as V

== Cryptographic Responsibilities ==

note over I
Issuer (Telco Operator)
-----------------------
• Generates Ed25519 key pair  
• Publishes public key in DID Document  
• Signs Verifiable Credential (VC)  
• Maintains secure private key storage  
end note

note over H
Holder (Subscriber Wallet)
--------------------------
• Manages own Ed25519 key pair  
• Receives signed VC from Issuer  
• Builds Verifiable Presentation (VP)  
• Signs VP with private key  
• Reveals only selective claims  
end note

note over V
Verifier (Service)
------------------
• Resolves DID Documents  
• Fetches Issuer/Holder public keys  
• Verifies VC & VP signatures  
• Confirms nonce + domain binding  
end note

== Example Structures ==

note over I
DID Document (Issuer)
---------------------
@context: https://www.w3.org/ns/did/v1
id: did:telco:airtel
publicKey:
  id: did:telco:airtel#key-1
  type: Ed25519VerificationKey2018
  controller: did:telco:airtel
  publicKeyJwk.x: <base64url(pubkey)>
end note

note over I
Verifiable Credential (VC)
--------------------------
@context: https://www.w3.org/2018/credentials/v1
id: did:telco:airtel:vc1234
type: ["VerifiableCredential", "SubscriberCredential"]
issuer: did:telco:airtel
credentialSubject:
  id: did:telco:harishm
  name: Harish M
  operator: Airtel
  circle: Karnataka
proof:
  type: JsonWebSignature2020
  created: 2025-11-07T10:00:00Z
  proofPurpose: assertionMethod
  verificationMethod: did:telco:airtel#key-1
  jws: <base64url(signature)>
end note

note over H
Verifiable Presentation (VP)
----------------------------
@context: https://www.w3.org/2018/credentials/v1
type: ["VerifiablePresentation"]
verifiableCredential: (reference to VC)
holder: did:telco:harishm
proof:
  type: JsonWebSignature2020
  created: 2025-11-07T10:05:00Z
  proofPurpose: authentication
  verificationMethod: did:telco:harishm#key-1
  domain: did:telco:verifier
  nonce: <random_nonce>
  jws: <base64url(holder_signature)>
end note

@enduml
